<p>The <strong>Headings</strong> module provides consistent, responsive
typography styles for HTML headings (<code>&lt;h1&gt;</code> through
<code>&lt;h6&gt;</code>) and corresponding utility classes
(<code>.h1</code> through <code>.h6</code>).</p>
